OL,5, More than 2,000 roles are at risk at   
OL,6, Tesco as it announces more changes to  
OL,7, the way it runs its supermarkets.      
OL,9,FThe grocer said it was planning to cut 
OL,10,F1,750 team manager roles across        
OL,11,Fhundreds of its larger stores, while   
OL,12,Fclosing positions elsewhere.           
OL,14,FTesco will instead introduce a new tier
OL,15,Fof shift leader roles which will take  
OL,16,Fover running its shop floor operations.
OL,18,FThe 1,800 new roles will be lower paid,
OL,19,Fbut managers who take the jobs will    
OL,20,Fhave their pay protected for two years.
